{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.400", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.360", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.120", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Verh\u00e4ltnis zwischen Arbeitszeit und freier Zeit treibt die Menschen um, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "insbesondere junge Menschen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei geht es um die Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der die Menschen zur Ruhe kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.440", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der sie Sport treiben oder sich ehrenamtlich engagieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Menschen m\u00fcssen auch putzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einkaufen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.840", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kochen und schlafen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.000", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie brauchen vor allem Zeit f\u00fcr ihre Kinder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Freunde oder Eltern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das alles macht ein gutes Leben aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Notwendig ist deshalb eine gute Balance; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.480", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn Arbeitszeit ist Lebenszeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.160", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichzeitig geht es auch um die Arbeitszeit im engeren Sinn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.520", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch hier besteht Handlungsbedarf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.240", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nach einer Studie der BAuA wollen 55\u00a0Prozent der Besch\u00e4ftigten ihre Arbeitszeit verk\u00fcrzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und 35\u00a0Prozent wollen sie verl\u00e4ngern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.760", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Andere sind mit dem Zeitumfang zufrieden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.280", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00fcnschen sich aber beweglichere Arbeitszeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bed\u00fcrfnisse ver\u00e4ndern sich auch noch im Lebensverlauf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer Kinder bekommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.600", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "will anders arbeiten als beim Einstieg in das Berufsleben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.000", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frauen wollen nicht mehr auf dem beruflichen Abstellgleis landen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie Kinder bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele junge M\u00e4nner wollen nicht mehr nur Feierabend- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.440", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Wochenendv\u00e4ter sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern sich gleichberechtigt um die Kinder k\u00fcmmern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.520", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir also ben\u00f6tigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.680", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind beweglichere Arbeitszeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.000", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit Arbeit besser ins Leben passt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.520", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So sehen wir Gr\u00fcne die Lage rund um die Arbeitszeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.880", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lese ich den Antrag der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.280", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann stelle ich fest, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.800", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir stellenweise wohl das Gleiche meinen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber es h\u00f6rt sich ganz anders an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dementsprechend haben wir unterschiedliche Herangehensweisen und andere Konzepte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.800", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei uns stehen die Besch\u00e4ftigten im Mittelpunkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.760", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht uns um ihre W\u00fcnsche und ihre Vorstellungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.200", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie arbeiten und leben wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb wollen wir den Besch\u00e4ftigten mehr Zeitsouver\u00e4nit\u00e4t erm\u00f6glichen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.560", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganz dringend notwendig ist ein R\u00fcckkehrrecht auf Vollzeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.720", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar f\u00fcr alle; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da sind wir uns einig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss Schluss sein mit der Formel \u201eeinmal Teilzeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.800", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "immer Teilzeit\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.000", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist frauenpolitisch extrem wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.120", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor allem aber sollen die Besch\u00e4ftigten mehr Einfluss nehmen k\u00f6nnen auf die Gestaltung ihrer Arbeitszeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar ganz konkret auf den Umfang, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.560", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Lage und den Ort. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier wollen wir die Rechte der Besch\u00e4ftigten st\u00e4rken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.600", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entsprechende Forderungen fehlen in dem vorliegenden Antrag leider komplett. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Solche Rechte sind aber wichtig; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn nur so entsteht tats\u00e4chlich mehr Lebensqualit\u00e4t."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.920", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen fordert Die Linke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.080", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die H\u00f6chstarbeitszeit auf 40\u00a0Stunden abgesenkt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.200", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beispielsweise bei prek\u00e4rer Besch\u00e4ftigung oder beim Arbeitsschutz muss der Gesetzgeber klare Grenzen ziehen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.440", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist selbstverst\u00e4ndlich\u00a0\u2013; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.920", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber bei der Arbeitszeit geht es um einen Ordnungsrahmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Ausgestaltung ist dann Sache der Sozialpartner; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.080", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das zeigt ja die IG\u00a0Metall momentan wunderbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.240", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insofern lehnen auch wir Gr\u00fcnen diese Forderung ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.360", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das passt auch zu unserer eigenen Forderung; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.960", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn wir wollen die Zeitsouver\u00e4nit\u00e4t f\u00fcr die Besch\u00e4ftigten erh\u00f6hen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.120", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das funktioniert eben nicht in einem engen und starren Rahmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.040", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich brauchen die Besch\u00e4ftigten Schutz; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.160", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber er ist gegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil neben der w\u00f6chentlichen auch noch die t\u00e4gliche H\u00f6chstarbeitszeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.520", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ruhezeiten und auch die Sonntagsruhe im Arbeitszeitgesetz geregelt sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss auch so bleiben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.680", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sage ich in Richtung SPD im Hinblick auf die Koalitionsverhandlungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.000", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen die Besch\u00e4ftigten nicht einschr\u00e4nken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern ihnen passende L\u00f6sungen bei der Arbeitszeit erm\u00f6glichen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.640", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.240", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.840", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Arbeitszeit ist Lebenszeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.440", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alles Weitere\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.240", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr mehr reicht die Zeit jetzt einfach nicht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.280", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diskutieren wir dann im Ausschuss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.360", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin mir sicher: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.680", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird spannend."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.440", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.040", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.320", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beate M\u00fcller-Gemmeke.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.760", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat jetzt zu seiner ersten Rede im Bundestag der fraktionslose Kollege Mario Mieruch."
   ]
  }
 ]
}